---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Disclaimer | ZynfexGame" description="Legal disclaimer regarding third-party games and content on ZynfexGame.">
	<div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto py-12 px-6 lg:px-8">
		<h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-8">Disclaimer</h1>
        
        <div class="prose prose-invert max-w-none text-gray-300">
            <p>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString()}</p>
            
            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">1. Third-Party Games and Intellectual Property</h2>
            <p>
                ZynfexGame acts as an aggregate platform that embeds and hosts free-to-play HTML5 web games sourced legally through open web distribution networks (such as GameDistribution) and developers who provide their games for public embedding on web portals. 
            </p>
            <p>
                We do not claim ownership, copyright, or intellectual property rights over the games, characters, branding, or assets hosted within our platform. All respective copyrights and trademarks are the property of their original developers and publishers.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">2. "As Is" Content</h2>
            <p>
                All games and content on ZynfexGame are provided on an "as is" and "as available" basis. While we strive to manually curate safe and family-friendly games, ZynfexGame makes no warranties, either express or implied, regarding the continuous availability, safety, or accuracy of the hosted games.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">3. External Links and Advertisements</h2>
            <p>
                Our gaming platform generates revenue through third-party advertising networks (e.g., Google AdSense). ZynfexGame has no direct control over the specific content of these advertisements or the external links they direct to based on an individual user's browsing profile.
            </p>

            <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mt-8 mb-4">4. Takedown Requests (DMCA)</h2>
            <p>
                ZynfexGame fully respects the intellectual property rights of developers and publishers. If you represent a game developer or publisher and believe that your copyrighted content is being embedded or displayed on our platform without valid authorization, please contact us immediately through our Contact Us portal for an expedited takedown.
            </p>
        </div>
	</div>
</Layout>
